A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the Georgia Pharmacy Association upon its 150th anniversary; and for other
2 purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Georgia Pharmacy Association was founded in October 1875 in Macon,
4 Georgia, by a group of Georgia pharmacists working to further the interests of pharmacy in
5 the state; and
6 WHEREAS, the Georgia Pharmacy Association advocates tirelessly for all involved in the
7 practice of pharmacy, including independent pharmacists, chain retail pharmacists, hospital
8 pharmacists, pharmacy technicians, pharmacy owners, and pharmacy students; and
9 WHEREAS, the association has been responsible for advances in education in pharmacy in
10 Georgia, including establishing the first guidelines for pharmacy education and licensure in
11 Georgia; and
12 WHEREAS, pharmacists in Georgia have been leaders in innovation and discovery,
13 especially in the formulation of products such as Coca-Cola and RC Cola; and
